      • mergeProcedures

        public void mergeProcedures(Package pkg)
        This merges all the procedures for another package into the current package. The example is if you have a Database Object and a Database View. The Database View has some extra stored procedures so you add the additional stored procedures to the package.
        Parameters:
        pkg -
